[117816648857231545076,100442351105407300771,Ballenberg offers a wonderful variety of old farmhouses from all across Switzerland which can be viewed from top to bottom, in a natural setting which is simply breathtaking. There are culinary options for any budget, ranging from a full three course meal to a quick, tasty snack. The sanitary facilities were very clean and evenly spaced. It is a perfect place to spend a relaxed day with the family.]
